{"id:": "/div[1]", "tag": "div", "attributes": {"type": "article", "{http://www.w3.org/XML/1998/namespace}id": "MG-1678-06_203", "resp": "mercure"}, "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]", "tag": "head", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/head[1]/text()[1]", "text": "[Vers sur le sujet de la Paix]"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]", "tag": "bibl", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]", "tag": "title", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/title[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Mercure galant"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/bibl[1]/text()[1]", "text": ", juin 1678 [tome 6], p. 203-207."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[1]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[1]/text()[1]", "text": "La Paix qu’on a tout lieu d’esperer, nous produira d’autres avantages. Il y a longtemps que nos Ennemis reconnoissoient qu’elle leur estoit necessaire ; mais sçavez-vous pourquoy elle commençoit à le devenir pour nous ? Vous l’allez apprendre par les Vers qui suivent."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]", "tag": "quote", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[1]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Apres tant de Combats qu’a suivis la Victoire,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[2]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[2]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[2]/text()[1]", "text": "On a grand besoin de la Paix,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[3]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[3]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[3]/text()[1]", "text": "Car le Parnasse desormais"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[4]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[4]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[4]/text()[1]", "text": "Ne sçait comment chanter la gloire"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[5]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[5]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[5]/text()[1]", "text": "Du plus Grand Roy qui fut jamais."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[6]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[6]/text()[1]", "text": "L’Hipocrene est à sec, & les Vallons Poëtiques"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[7]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[7]/text()[1]", "text": "Ont cent fois retenty des vieux Panegyriques"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[8]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[8]/text()[1]", "text": "Qu’on presentoit jadis aux plus fameux Guerriers."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[9]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[9]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[9]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "Loüis"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sc"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[9]/text()[1]", "text": " a flétry leurs Lauriers."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[10]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[10]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[10]/text()[1]", "text": "Il fait plus qu’on ne peut écrire,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[11]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[11]/text()[1]", "text": "Chacun est épuisé, l’on ne sçait plus que dire,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[12]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[12]/text()[1]", "text": "Apollon est confus, & Pegase recrû."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[13]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[13]/text()[1]", "text": "Mais graces à la Paix il va reprendre haleine."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[14]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[14]/text()[1]", "text": "Nostre Grand Roy, dit-on, quand on l’a le moins crû,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[15]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[15]/text()[1]", "text": "Plante des Oliviers sur les bords de la Seine."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[16]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[16]/text()[1]", "text": "Las de vaincre, il renonce enfin à foudroyer."}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[17]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[17]/text()[1]", "text": "Courage, Beaux Esprits, reprenez l’Ecritoire,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[18]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[18]/text()[1]", "text": "Consacrez à l’envy vos talens à sa gloire,"}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[19]", "tag": "l", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[19]/space[1]", "tag": "space", "children": []}, {"id": "/div[1]/quote[1]/l[19]/text()[1]", "text": "Ils ne peuvent mieux s’employer."}]}]}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[2]", "tag": "p", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/text()[1]", "text": "Ces Vers m’ont esté envoyez de Dieppe, & sont de M"}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/hi[1]", "tag": "hi", "children": [{"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/hi[1]/text()[1]", "text": "r"}], "attributes": {"rend": "sup"}}, {"id": "/div[1]/p[2]/text()[2]", "text": " Merville, qui dans une fort grande jeunesse fait connoistre par tout ce qu’il fait qu’il est né pour la Poësie."}]}]}